Welcome back to Earth, Bob and Doug! For the first time in history, a commercial company—entrusted to carry @NASA astronauts to and from the @ISS—has successfully taken humans to orbit and back on the world's most advanced rocket and spacecraft.

Falcon 9 lifts off from historic Launch Complex 39A and sends Crew Dragon to orbit on its first flight with @NASA astronauts to the @iss
